            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高力(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8996:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8996\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8996-TW</a>)14日10:00股價下跌44元，報511.0元，跌幅7.93%，成交528張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高力(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8996:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8996\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8996-TW</a>)所屬產業為電機機械，主要業務為板式熱交換器。熱能產品。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌16.16%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.01%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+708 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,155 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-1,120 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+673 張</li> <li>融資增減：-1,032 張</li> <li>融券增減：-261 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
